VALUES ('36mm Rolex Watch with Stainless Steel Jubilee Band + 14k white gold and diamond Bracelet (Father`s Day Special)', '36mm-rolex-watch-with-stainless-steel-jubilee-band-14k-white-gold-and-diamond-bracelet-father-s-day-special', '<p>Look stunning with this luxurious set of timeless jewelry. This collection includes 4 piece deal:</p>
