VALUES ('24mm Rolex with Stainless steel oyster band + White gold and diamond Band + 14k white gold and diamond Earrings + Gift', '24mm-rolex-with-stainless-steel-oyster-band-white-gold-and-diamond-band-14k-white-gold-and-diamond-earrings-gift', '<p>Look stunning with this luxurious set of timeless jewelry. This collection includes 4 piece deal:</p>
