<p>Enjoy long-lasting brilliance and class with this set.<br></p>
<p><span>4) </span>Comes with<span> </span>a surprise gift <span>from Marchello the Jeweler. </span></p>', 6900, '["https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0255/6044/9109/files/WhatsAppImage2025-03-29at5.54.30PM.jpg?v=1743285302","https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0255/6044/9109/files/WhatsAppImage2025-03-29at5.54.31PM.jpg?v=1743285302","https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0255/6044/9109/files/WhatsAppImage2025-03-29at5.54.32PM_1.jpg?v=1743285302","https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0255/6044/9109/files/WhatsAppImage2025-03-29at5.54.32PM.jpg?v=1743285302"]'::jsonb, true, 10, '24mm Rolex with Stainless steel oyster band + White gold and diamond Band + 14k white gold and diamond Earrings + Gift', '24mm Rolex with Stainless steel oyster band + White gold and diamond Band + 14k white gold and diamond Earrings + Gift | Lumina Luxe Jewels', 'Look stunning with this luxurious set of timeless jewelry. This collection includes 4 piece deal:
